      scope: "Fixed PEP 691 §3.2 yanked field accept bool-or-string-reason (+168/-16 LOC across 2 files). **src/pkgmgr/simple_api.rs** (+133/-8): added `#[serde(untagged)] enum YankedValue { Bool(bool), Reason(String) }` + changed `Pep691File.yanked` from strict `bool` to `Option<YankedValue>`; `to_file_entry` flattens with PEP 592 semantics — None→(false,None), Bool(b)→(b,None), Reason(s)→(true,Some(s)) (reason-presence implies yanked=true); HTML parser (parse_simple_html) rewrote data-yanked extraction from presence-only to 3-way VALUE match: None→(false,None), Some('')→(true,None), Some(reason)→(true,Some(reason.to_string())). Added 2 unit tests in pkgmgr::simple_api::tests: (1) test_parse_pep691_json_with_string_yanked_reason — fixture with 4 yanked states (bool true / string reason / bool false / absent), asserts correct (yanked, yanked_reason) split per REQ R5/AC2; (2) test_parse_simple_html_yanked_attr_with_reason — 3 HTML states (absent/empty/non-empty data-yanked), asserts HTML parser behavior per REQ R3/AC3. **tests/pypi_index_client_integration.rs** (+35/-8): added IT-07 it_07_fetch_metadata_simple_requests_handles_string_yanked live-PyPI test per AC1 — calls fetch_metadata_simple('requests'), asserts Ok + source='simple-api' + ≥1 file with yanked=true AND non-empty yanked_reason (validates YankedValue enum on real PyPI response containing CVE-2024-35195-mitigation yank string); updated IT-06 NOTE comment removing 'parser bug tracked separately; IT-06 pivoted to fetch_metadata' language (per AC4/R4), replaced with clean rationale 'Uses fetch_metadata (JSON primary + Simple fallback) to exercise the JSON API path. The Simple API string-yanked path is exercised separately in IT-07.'; also refreshed the top-of-file Tests manifest comment block adding IT-07 line with aligned column formatting. **Agent report**: score-change-implementation agent a59609462e2acf28f completed cleanly first-shot (29 tool uses, 327269ms total, 43530 total tokens). Reported test results: unit 11/11 pass (9 pre-existing + 2 new); integration 7/7 pass (IT-01→IT-07 all green against live pypi.org). types.rs untouched — yanked_reason: Option<String> already exists on ReleaseFile per ref context. Agent respected out-of-scope: no JSON fetch_metadata path changes, no retry/fallback changes, no FileEntry public-shape churn. Explicitly reported: 'No commit created — git mutations blocked for this agent role per three-role contract R10'; mainthread committed agent work with suggested message."
      commit: df88430a   # `fix(mamba-pkgmgr): accept PEP 691 string-yanked reason in Simple API parser` — applied by mainthread per R10 (agent cannot commit)
